<li id="cite_note-46"><span class="mw-cite-backlink noprint"><a href="#cite_ref-46">↑</a> </span><span class="reference-text"><span class="citation not_fr_quote" lang="en">«&#160;<span class="italique">[...]so brutal and disturbing that it appears to warp time before and after into a single unwavering line of fate.</span>&#160;»</span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-Hevesi-47"><span class="mw-cite-backlink noprint"><a href="#cite_ref-Hevesi_47-0">↑</a> </span><span class="reference-text"><span class="ouvrage" id="Hevesi1988"><span class="ouvrage" id="Dennis_Hevesi1988">Dennis <span class="nom_auteur">Hevesi</span>, «&#160;<cite style="font-style:normal;">Toni Morrison's Novel 'Beloved' Wins the Pulitzer Prize in Fiction</cite>&#160;», <i>The New York Times</i>,&#8206; <time class="nowrap" datetime="1988-04-01" data-sort-value="1988-04-01"><abbr class="abbr" title="premier">1<sup>er</sup></abbr> avril 1988</time> <small style="line-height:1em;">(<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.nytimes.com/1988/04/01/nyregion/toni-morrison-s-novel-beloved-wins-the-pulitzer-prize-in-fiction.html">lire en ligne</a>, consulté le <span class="nowrap">29 avril 2017</span>)</small><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Toni+Morrison%27s+Novel+%27Beloved%27+Wins+the+Pulitzer+Prize+in+Fiction&amp;rft.jtitle=The+New+York+Times&amp;rft.aulast=Hevesi&amp;rft.aufirst=Dennis&amp;rft.date=1988-04-01&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1988%2F04%2F01%2Fnyregion%2Ftoni-morrison-s-novel-beloved-wins-the-pulitzer-prize-in-fiction.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Ffr.wikipedia.org%3AToni+Morrison"></span></span></span></span>
